text: Way Out West is American country singer Marty Stuart's 18th studio album released in 2017. The album was produced by Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers guitarist Mike Campbell. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ===Marty Stuart & His Fabulous Superlatives=== *Chris Scruggs - bass guitar, vocals *Harry Stinson - drums, vocals *Marty Stuart - acoustic guitar, electric guitar, vocals *Kenny Vaughan - electric guitar, vocals ==References== Category:2017 albums Category:Marty Stuart albums
title: Way Out West (Marty Stuart album)
